Class Description
InvalidMazeException
The base exception class for all maze related exceptions.
Maze
Class to construct and represent the maze
Maze.Direction
Enum to represent the 4 different directions that a the route can travel
MazeVisualiser
Class to create a javafx GridPane to represent the current maze state
MultipleEntranceException
Exception to be thrown when maze contains multiple entrances
MultipleExitException
Exception to be thrown when maze contains multiple exits
NoEntranceException
Exception to be thrown when maze contains no entrances
NoExitException
Exception to be thrown when maze contains no exits
NoRouteFoundException
Exception to be thrown when the route finder cannot find a route
RaggedMazeException
Exception to be thrown when the mazes rows or columns are uneven
RouteFinder
Route find contains the current route the checked tiles and the methods to search the maze for an exit from the entrance
Tile
Tile class represents an indiviaual tile in the maze
Tile.Type
Enum to represent the 4 different types of tile
